                    The Aloop 4SMX XR250 or XR400 seat/tank kit costs just $599 plus shipping and is available online.
                </h2>
                <p class="lead fw-normal text-muted">
                    Featured on the cover of the April 1998 Dirt Bike Magazine and the cover of the May 1998 Motocross Action Magazine, and more than 8 other Offroad Magazine covers worldwide, ALOOP's XR400 Seat Tank kit is a "must-have" item for any XR400 performance rider.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>



