    <div class="container px-5 my-5">
        <div class="text-center">
            <h2 class="fw-bolder">What's in the Box?</h2>
            <p class="lead fw-normal text-muted mb-5">
                The kit consists of a 2.0 gallon motocross tank (just .8 gallon less than the stock tank), a new seat with CR-style foam and a Guts Racing non-slip seat cover, and two CR-style radiator shrouds complete with genuine Guts graphics. The new tank is set up to use two fuel petcocks for better fuel delivery under race conditions. Most importantly, the ALOOP Tank allows the rider to sit more than 3 inches further forward, more than an inch higher, and the tank is more than three inches narrower at the knees.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
